The goal of the game is to hurl the acrobat alien into the waiting paddling pool on every level. A range of tools to help you overcome obstacles and achieve the right momentum are at your disposal.
In 25 challenging levels, you can throw the alien about with unicycles, trampolines, and even a giant cannon to finish the level with a stunt-worthy splash into the paddling pool.  Play Circus is now for free and have hours of fun!

games.title: Bridge Hero
games.description:
Did you ever admire the bold people that build bridges over the deepest valleys. Even though the job is incredibly dangerous, you can now experience it from the safety of your couch with Bridge Hero.
In this fun online game building bridges is easy 1, 2, 3. Just tap at the screen, hold on a bit to stretch the bridge element and let go when you think it is long enough to reach the next platform. Be careful though! If your bridge element is too short or the too long the construction worker will inevitably fall and your game is over. How far can you make it?

games.title: Cake Shop
games.description:
Did you ever dream about being a confectioner and running your own cake shop?  Do you know every recipe by heart and fantasize about fruits, buttercream and fancy toppings? Now here's your chance to make your dream come true at last! You start your business small with just one kind of cake but within short time you will find your yourself offering the most different cakes, tasty juice and even fast food snacks.
But be aware, that your customers will get angry, if you do not manage to serve them in time. So be quick, be well organized and soon your business will thrive. You will have tons of fun in this Diner Dash inspired free online game!

games.title: Retry Again
games.description:
Retry Again is one of the hottest games of the year!  You're steering a frail, smoky and barely controllable plane desperately trying to reach your destination, before the flying coffin craters into the ground. But of course you will crash. Time and again. And just when you think you can't take it anymore and you are ready to give up, you will successfully manage the level and move on to crash some more. 
8-bit  graphics and a catchy synthesizer soundtrack bring the look and feel of the beloved arcade classics from the 80s. Retry Again features 18 levels packed with fun and frustration. Will you be able to beat all levels and collect all the hidden coins?

games.title: Catch The Frog
games.description:
Do you need to kill some time? Or do you look for a fun game to have a blast with? Catch The Frog will leave no room for boredom! In this free online game you accompany the frog through 36 mini games full of fun and variety. Some level will test your reactions while others need great perception or perfect timing.
If you manage to master all levels from a group, you unlock the next series of six mini games. Are you able to solve all of them? Whether you are playing on your phone, a tablet or on your desktop computer, you can play Catch The Frog right now with no downloads,  no installs and no costs.

games.title: Juicy Berries
games.description:
In this free online game everything revolves around juicy berries and how to collect them. Following the much-loved match3 gameplay you have to look for at least three berries of the same color lying next to each other and tap on them to harvest the berries. To collect even more berries in one move you should try to get those berries with a bonus modifier.
With every berry you collect, you do not only come closer to solving a level, but you also earn a tiny little bit of mighty boosters. These boosters can save your day if you run in trouble getting a level done by adding extra moves or collecting all berries from one color.

games.title: Squirrel Hero
games.description:
Help the cute Squirrel Hero to defend their tree against strange alien creatures that come floating through the air and attack the squirrels home. The bravest of the squirrels fight the aliens be jumping at their heads from above and prevent them from passing the tree house.
In 25 exciting levels you fight a rearguard battle as more and more creatures attack and the squirrels have to climb higher and higher into the treetops. The higher you get, the cooler extras you will find and the more power-ups you are able to afford. Freeze your enemies, slow them down or even throw bombs at them. Kaboom!

games.title: Toss a Paper 2
games.description:
It's one of these days at the office, right? Maybe there is so much work to do that even starting to do it is not worth the bother - or there is literally nothing to do for you and you struggle not to fall asleep. But fear not, we got the solution for your problem!  Get ready to play the ultimate office game at three brand new locations.
Grab a cup of coffee, virtually crumple up a piece of paper in this fun online game and see if you can throw it into the small trash can on the other side of your room! If you managed to do so even with the electric fan blowing and giving the paper spin, it is time to move on to much larger places, like the office storage and the underground parking garage.

games.title: Dots
games.description:
Dots is one of those rare games that you fire up to kill a few minutes of spare time and that you end up playing for hours and hours. You have to connect dots of the same color in order to make them vanish. For every dot you manage to clear, you score points and you have to achieve a certain score within sixty second to pass the level. If you form a loop all dots of the same color will disappear at a single blow. Extras like the ability to clear a single dot from the play field or to stop the time for a few seconds give you the much needed edge if it looks like your badly off.
Play this highly addictive puzzle game now online and completely for free!

games.title: Let  Them Fight
games.description:
What would you do if a couple of many-eyed aliens start to spit their spawn at you? Would you be too scared to do anything about it? Or even run away screaming like a banshee? Maybe you should. After all that would be a very reasonable thing to do. Or should you try to be a hero and fight the spawn with your bare hands? No way, you can't touch this alien thingies, they are dangerous! The sensible thing to do is to grab your mallet and knock the aliens out. Stop! Hammer time! Bump! Bump! Bump! Now why would you ever stop doing this?
Play Let Them Fight now for free and find out how long you can hold back the aliens!

games.title: Dads Long Legs
games.description:
The objective of Dads Long Legs seems to be the most simple task you've got in a game: Take some steps and see how far you can go. After all, you managed to learn how to walk long time ago, right? So how hard can it be in a game? Just tap or click to put one leg in front of the other...
In reality you will fall down time and again before you are able to make even a few proud steps. You will learn that even the tiniest mistake will make you come crushing down to the floor. And then you will try again and again, because Dads Long Legs hits the perfect sweet spot right in between fun, frustration and motivation! Play it now!

games.title: Animalines
games.description:
Are you looking for a brain teaser game with a fresh idea? Here comes Animalines! Click or tap on an animal and drag it to the second animal of the same kind. Cover as much tiles as possible on your way while still leaving room to connect all pairs. To clear the level you have to use all the blocks on the play field and to earn an award you are only allowed to do one move per pair.
Animalines is packed with incredible 75 levels that will make your brain run hot and guarantee fun for hours and hours. Play now and experience the ultimate challenge!

games.title: No Dots
games.description:
No Dots is the quintessential puzzle game where you need ouside-the-box thinking, a colorful and fun brain teaser that is easy to pick up but offers deep and entertaining gameplay for endless hours. On a six by six board you have to place colored badges straight or around the corner and try to create matches of three or more badges of the same color. The more badges you manage to match and remove the more points you score. With time more and more colors will come into play and it will get hard to place them on the board without blocking yourself.
Play No Dots now for free and make sure to cancel your plans for the coming days - you will not able to stop playing!

games.title: Magic Card Saga
games.description:
Magic Card Saga takes you to a journey of card game challenges under the baking sun of the caribic. The game is loosely based on the classic Solitaire rules. To clean up the field you can collect cards that are one above or below your base card.  
To make things even more fun, you can buy helpful extras from the points you earned. A joker can be any card you want it to be, extra cards give you more flexibility and third extra card instantaneously unlocks the gold cards you have to capture to finish the level.
Will you make the right decisions and end the level with enough points to score three stars? Play now!

games.title: Tap the Mouse
games.description: Tap The Mouse is a collection of fun mini games that share a common goal: You have to find the white mouse and tap on it to finish the level. The most different objectives guarantee fun and challenges for hours without getting bored of doing the same things over and over again. Be amazed by 24 levels full of games that tease your brain or test you reactions - and of course don't forget to Tap The Mouse! Play now online at the world's largest HTML5 games platform! No downloads and no installs, no costs.

games.title: Farm Puzzle Story 2
games.description: Farm Puzzle Story 2 is an awesome matching casual game! Use your amazing skills to tap and combine the vegetables. Carrots, tomatoes, broccoli, potatoes and many other healthy vegetables await you in this fast paced and addicting game. Get mighty boosters at the beginning of each level and use them to win even the hardest battles - losing is not an option. Once you start playing, you will not be able to stop. Farm Puzzle Story is a FREE match-3 game that gives more 30 levels packed with fun und enjoyment! Put veggies together to earn apples and points! Don´t forget to control the number of moves left, because if you don't manage to combine vegetables well, you will run out of moves and lose. Be smart, be fast and win!

games.title: Do not Crash
games.description:
In this fast paced action game you drive around a very special race track. A race track with oncoming traffic. To make things worse the approaching cars change lanes every now and then and you have to pay attention and show lightning fast reflexes to thread your way through the them.
The game starts slow, but as the other cars gain speed and the field spreads over the track, you need to give everything to avoid a collision. The better you are, the more cars you unlock - play now online and absolutely for free - and DO NOT CRASH!

games.title: Basketball Hoops
games.description: Are you stuck indoors, when all you really want to do is get out on the court and shoot some hoops? Of course you could just move on with your work and forget about basketball - or you could play Basketball Hoops for free. Show you mad skills in three different difficulty levels  and locations. The longer you play, the harder it will get to sink the ball in the basket, as the wind shear grows stronger and stronger. Are you cool headed enough to score constantly even under the most adverse conditions? Find out now and play Basketball Hoops online!

games.title: Watch Out 2
games.description: Watch Out 2 is the one of the most difficult and frustrating games you will ever come across. But it is also one of the most fun and motivating games because success depends on nothing but your own skill. There are no unfair challenges or even cheating enemies, if YOU do well, you will succeed. Playing Watch Out 2 can train your reaction time as well as your perception. After playing for a while you will find that you are able to reach scores you never thought to be attainable. For the best of the best there is the even more infuriating hard mode. Impossible you say? Try harder!

games.title: Treasure Miner
games.description: Be a real Treasure Miner in this free online game and pull all sorts of riches out of the soil - you'll dig it! While other miners drive tunnels into the mountains you mine the cool way! You just ram your hook into the ground and pull up whatever ores or gem you are able to grab within sixty seconds.  To help you maximize your profit you can invest the points you've earned in helpful tools like a better hook, bombs to blow up the useless rocks in your way, some extra time or the ability to pull your hook back faster. Play now see if you can be one of the few miners who actually get rich!

games.title: Jelly Slice
games.description:
Sticky fingers and gelatin desserts! Jelly Slice is a unique brain and puzzle game in which you use your fingers to slice the jelly and collect the stars.
There is only one rule: Slice the jelly so that each slice contains only one star.
Sounds simple? You will need a good dose of creativity and skill as you progress. 
Do you think you can get a perfect score for every level by collecting all the stars? Find out now. 
This free version of Jelly Slice will take you through 3 jelly packs for a total of 60 sticky levels filled with challenge and fun. Get ready for some slicing action!

games.title: Fists of Frenzy
games.description:
You are on your own at a crossroad and you are surrounded by fierce ninjas. The ninjas will come after you from all directions and you need perfect timing to fight them off. Once they are right next to you, there is a small moment in time to kick in the direction of an attacker to neutralise him, before he is able to stab you. From time to time you fall in a frenzy that clears off all enemies at once and gives you some badly needed time to tense up and concentrate.
The more enemies you managed to defeat, the cooler character you are able to unlock and play with. Be it a monk, the schoolgirl, a panda or even a robot - whatever you play, fun is guaranteed in this free online game. Play now!

games.title: Timbermen Halloween
games.description:
Even though it is Halloween time, you should not be afraid to go out in the spooky woods and cut some serious wood! In this free online game you will meet the most strange people. Vlad Dracula, Witches and even Death himself are out there with you, to swing the axe and turn even the biggest trees into firewood. But be aware to not get hit by branches while you do your work.
The further you cut the woods, the stranger halloween costumes you can get and the more powerful you will be. There is always room for improvement and you got to ignore the spooky tension in the woods and go the extra mile, to get those trees to the ground!

games.title: Pandalicious
games.description:
Collect delicious fruits and feed them to the cute panda in this free online game! Tap and hold to connect the fruits and release to finally collect them and let the panda enjoy the glorious, juicy fruitiness. You can connect fruits of the same type diagonally or in a straight line and should strive to to harvest the longest chains possible, as you receive bonus points and more time if you manage to connect more than five fruits at a time.
In each level you have to collect a number of different fruits to make the panda happy and of course you have to be quick about it, because the time is ticking away fast.

games.title: The Tower
games.description: Who would have thought, that building an entire skyscraper could be that easy? In this awesome action game that is inspired by the legendary Tower Bloxx you stack up the floors to form a building. Of course you have to make sure to place one floor exactly on another, not only because you get heaps of coins for every perfectly placed block, but also because the game gets faster and faster with every miss.  The higher your multistory building gets, the more coins you will be able to hoard and the more cool boosters you will be able to buy. Play Towers now for free and find out, if you have what it takes to beat the highscore and to set the highest tower that in the history of mankind.

games.title: Cat's Hunger
games.description: Cats Hunger is the purrfect game for all you cat loving people out there.  In this brain teasing game you feed fish to the hungry kittens. Each cat  eats all the fish in a certain path and you need to make sure, that all the fish on the field gets eaten. If that does seem easy to you, you should think again, because there are things that distract your kitties or change their path. The card box never fails to stop the playful furballs and of course they have to go through the drain pipe regardless where it leads them. Play Cats Hunger now for free, you will love the cute cats and the challenging gameplay.

games.title: Candy Rain 2
games.description:
Everyone likes candies, don't we? Now here is Candy Rain 2, that is all sweets but no calories! In this beautiful and challenging match-three video game it is your task to combine at least three of the delicious sweets to make them disappear. If you play smart and manage to make more candy vanish with one move or even trigger combos that make different sorts of candy vanish, you can get tons of extra points and useful boosters, that make it much easier to achieve the levels goals. Always have an eye on the scores though, as you only have a limited amount of moves to reach win the level.
Play the wonderful Candy Rain 2 now online and for free!

games.title: Flag Trivia
games.description:
How good is your knowledge about country flags? Find out in this fun, free online game! Right now there are not less than 193 different countries in the world - do you think you know all their flags? 
You start the game easy by choosing flags from Northern America or Europe, but as you progress through all the continents, you will have to identify the flags from countries that you might not even have heard of. If you managed to guess the right country the game provides you with handy information about the different countries, such as the population, the size or the capital.

games.title: Feed Me
games.description:
Feed Me is the fantastic, free online game where cute graphics meet challenging gameplay that will make your brain run hot in no time. The goal of the game is to arrange different elements in order to not only feed the tasty candy to the ever-hungry monster, but also to collect as many stars as possible on the way. Pads can change the direction of the flying candy, card boxes let the candy bounce back and this is only the beginning.
 40 level s packed with the perfect mixture of tons of fun and a tiny bit of frustration will keep you hooked to your screen and entertained for hours and hours.

games.title: Pudding Land
games.description: How many of the funny wiggling puddings can you make disappear in this fun, free online game? Inspired by the gameplay of the famous Diamond Dash it is your task to combine three puddings of the same color. If you manage to combine even more of the same color you get special puddings as a reward, that can help you to reach the levels goals and clear the playing field. Additionally you can invest your game credits in extras from the shop. Whether you are playing against the clock or if you have to solve the level with a given number of moves, once you enter one the more than thirty levels of Pudding Land fun is guaranteed.

games.title: Mahjong Adventure
games.description:
Play the ancient Chinese game of Mah Jong in this free online game! The objective of the game is to clear the playfield by matching pairs of tiles. This sounds easy, but of course there is a problem: You can only choose from those tiles, that are free, which means that they have to lie on the edge of a row.
In this adventure style game you guide the young sorceress through forty increasingly challenging levels that guarantee fun for hours and hours. If you manage to solve the puzzles fast as lightning you will be rewarded with up to three stars for each level. Do you manage to get all of them?

games.title: Bubble Shooter
games.description: Bubble Shooter is a fast paced match-3 arcade puzzle game that takes the gameplay of the much-loved Puzzle Bobble to a whole new level by adding cool extras. The thirty levels start easy, but as you progress through the game  you will need every bit of help you can get. From the credits you earn, you can buy cool stuff like a bomb to clear a whole area, more bubbles to shoot or bubbles that fit to every color they cling onto. If you manage to separate bubbles by popping every bubble above them, they will turn in to juicy fruits that give you just as fruity bonus points.

games.title: Doodle Connect
games.description: Doodle Connect is the perfect game to pass the time. Attractive graphics in the popular doodle style, a simple concept and tricky puzzles await you! Tricky puzzles? How hard can it be to connect a couple of dots with a continuous line? But once you’ve tried, and failed, to draw the infamous “Santa’s House” a couple of times, you’ll know that the answer is: pretty hard. Starting with simple shapes, the aim is to complete almost fifty levels of increasingly complex pictures - your head will soon start to spin.

games.title: Don't Tap
games.description:
Don't Tap condenses the basic idea of ground breaking game hits like Rock Band or Guitar Hero into a simple yet genius free online game that you can enjoy, whether you play on your phone, a tablet or on your desktop.
Not less than six fun and thrilling game modes - each with three difficulty levels wait - for you to discover them. You have to touch the black tiles as they move past the screen to play world-famous tunes. In some game modes these tiles come faster and faster at you while in others you have to play as many notes, as you can in a given time - but one thing is the same in all game modes: Play a single wrong note and it is "Game over", so be careful!

games.title: Swing Copters
games.description:
Get airborne and reach for the skies in this free online game! You can control the bold pilot by tapping on your screen! Be careful while trying to avoid obstacles and flying through gates just like you did in the much-loved Flappy Bird game. A single tap on your screen changes the direction of your character so be careful when to tap, because without skill and a bit of luck your flight will come to a very sudden end at one of the gates or at the hammers that swing right through your way.
Just like Flappy Bird this game is a highly addictive blend of fun and frustration, the simple yet extremely hard will keep you hooked for hours and hours. You can get the highscore!

games.title: Slinguin
games.description: Help the hungry Pinguin to get the fish. Debris, dangerous icicles and even other animals stand between our little pinguin and the delicious fish and only you can help the poor thing.

games.title: Submarine Dash
games.description: Take your seat in your own submarine and swim through a beautiful underwater world in this all new and mega fun endless game with many cool features! Enjoy intuitive submarine controls by lifting your finger to sink down and touching the display to let it rise up again. Along your exciting adventure try to collect as many coins and fun power-ups as possible to buy powerful upgrades! Your ultimate goal is to transform your basic submarine into a high tech one! This fun and exciting game is all about speed and your hand eye skill. Get ready to explore the ocean, but be aware of enemy rockets, dangerous rocks and other obstacles!

games.title: Pirate Bay
games.description: Help to defend the pirate bay by shooting down all the enemy ships! Since every ship is vulnerable to different things, you need to destroy it using a different ammunition from the cannons. As time passes more and more pirate ship will reach your shoreline and try to loot your city. You will need lightning fast reflexes and a fair bit of concentration to protect the riches you have gathered. Do you think you have what it takes, to stop them all? Or will you lose everything you own? Find out now and play this fun online game for free!

games.title: Timber Men
games.description: It's time to go out in the woods and cut some serious wood! In this free online game you get to live the life of a lumberjack! Swing your axe and turn even the biggest trees into firewood. But be aware to not get hit by branches while you do your work. The further you cut the woods, the better lumberjacks you can play. Be it a more powerful cut or a better axe, there is always room for improvement and you got to go the extra mile, to get those trees to the ground!

games.title: Sudoku Blitz
games.description:
It's not long since Sudoku has taken over the world of puzzle games in a lightning. Now it is time to take the experience to the next level and tease your brain with this free, entertaining online game! Sudoku Blitz adds all the fun and the challenge of an arcade game to the classic puzzle and brain teasing elements that made Sudoku an instant worldwide success. 
In two challenging game modes you place the falling pieces on the board following to the normal Sudoku rules, get bonuses for extra hard placements and try to fill the whole Sudoku board!

games.title: Make it Rain
games.description: From rags to riches! In this fun Cookieclicker style game you start out wit nothing and swipe your way to immense riches and the power that comes with that kind of money. How fast can you make it rain money and how much can you earn? Hundreds, thousands, millions, billions or even more? Start small by just swiping the screen and let your money pile up! Become rich by making business and financial investments or go into politics to earn money while you are sleeping! Swipe, swipe, swipe, swipe and don´t forget to swipe! And now have fun and take it away!

games.title: Carrot Cake
games.description: Treat yourself with a tasty, tasty carrot cake! Learn how to make the cake and then try to get it done faster and faster. With it's realistic interaction and the nice graphics playing this fun game will wet your appetite for a tasty carrot cake! But we got you covered - you can take the real recipe that is included and bake for you and your friends!

games.title: Farm Puzzle Story
games.description:
Are you able to Crush the farm? The brand new type of Match-3 gameplay will break your mind in this fun, free online game! Compete against the clock and maximize your points while matching crops! But at the same time you have remember to match a crop on each tile of the grid before the time runs out. Combined in one cute game, these two interesting game logics guarantee fun and challenges  for hours and hours. Play it now!
 To get the best experience we recommend to play Farm Puzzle Story on a tablet device or on your desktop computer.

games.title: Maya
games.description: Enjoy the best ZUMA style game with many attractive features and scenes! Shoot to match colored marbles or powerful lightnings in group of 3 or more to rake in as many points as possible. Swap balls and try to create combos in order to cause chain reactions and earn more rewarding power ups.  Unlock well-designed maps, to make the game more enjoyable, addictive and challenging. Earn experience as a ZUMA style player and try to complete all levels maximum performance ratings. However be careful and don´t let your chain reach the statue of the Mayan at the end of the trail or you will lose!

games.title: Sagemath
games.description: Sagemath will take you on a journey full of powerful magic spells and numbers! Use your math skills to defeat the approaching enemies by doing the correct calculations! Be fast and accurate or your enemies will crush you!

games.title: Animal Link
games.description: Get ready for the cuteness overload that is Animal Link! Animal Link is a fun puzzle game full of lovely creatures but it also needs a lot of skill to help animals. As the pups are not happy if the y are alone, you have to bring them together. Link the same two animals to make them happy and master all stages on the huge map! Buy upgrades from the store before each level and use them in case your time runs out! Do you have what it takes to make all your animals happy again?

games.title: Farm Jelly Puzzle
games.description:
It is time for your summer on the farm! Have a blast while connecting the different farm elements to make them vanish. Follow the popular match3 rules in this free online game, to successfully complete a level and to earn gold. But be smart with your effort, you only have so much moves to make a resource vanish from each and every tile of the field.
Fortunately you can re-invest your hard earned gold in mighty boosters and items like the tractor or the fork, that get rid of inconveniently placed resources and  help you to gain back control in situations that seemed impossible to solve.

games.title: Bombs and Zombies
games.description: Defend your village against zombie hordes using bombs, springs and shields! Earn money during each level and invest it wisely to buy new weapons and armor. Will you be able to stop the invasion?

games.title: Sweet Sorter
games.description: Sort the sweets through their different conveyor belts and make sure candies don't fall on the boxes that are not of their color. Enjoy the increasing challenge as more and faster conveyor belts unlock in this colorful game.

games.title: My Little Farm
games.description: Build stables with uncommon animals, create new fields, develop your farmhouse and provide clean energy to rebuild your little farm!

games.title: Monster Hunter
games.description: Defend your castle and don’t let the enemies breach the walls! Use your bow and arrow combined with your magical attacks to push back the hordes of evil! Earn gold, upgrade your skills and improve your castle to be victorious!

games.title: Crazy Birds
games.description:
Help the Crazy Birds to defend themselves! The pigs want to expel the birdies from their own land and did set up fortresses already. But these birds wouldn't be known as Crazy Birds, if some walls could hold them back! Whether it's wood or stone, for those birdies it doesn't matter, as they just dive into the walls head first and crush them.
And if they fail there always even crazier birds to follow. Use the different abilities of the crazy birds to defeat the army of enemy pigs. Set up the slingshot and get ready to aim, shoot and destroy all the enemy structures and angry pigs.

games.title: Toss a Paper
games.description:
You are stuck in the office again and you need to kill some time? As doing your daily work is not an option, it is time to get ready to play office games! Put your feet up, virtually crumple up a piece of paper in this fun online game and see if can throw it into the small trash can in your room! 
Easy enough you think? Well, think again! The electric fans blowing fresh air through your office will make  your task harder and harder as they power up over time. Don't give up and try to make the shot anyway!

games.title: Football Tricks
games.description: Take control of your team on the field! Perform awesome tricks and reinforce your team of champions to score goals from different positions!

games.title: Pet Crush Saga
games.description: Rescue the pets from the evil pet snatchers by removing the blocks from underneath them until they reach the bottom. Moves can be limited so plan your strategy carefully!

games.title: Madracer

games.title: Space Flight
games.description: Try dock as many ships possible in the spacestation. Be careful not to crash the shuttles as you guide them on there way to landing.

games.title: Sharks can fly
games.description: Drag Airfin, the shark, down and release him to let him fly. The point of each level is to collect all the clovers. Also watch out for the spikey turtles!

games.title: Brainie
games.description: It's not a shame to use your brain! This game will check your mad math skills. Select boxes to get a value shown in the bubble on the top of the Brainies head.  Select a combination of numbers to equal the number displayed on top to eliminate them. Get bonus points by selecting same color numbers. The game is over when the numbers pile all the way to the top.

games.title: Swamps Adventures
games.description: Jump your way through the swamp marshes and avoid or approach the alligators carefully to avoid been eaten.

games.title: Tetrix Pirates Tale
games.description: Help the pirates collect their tetrix gems by solving the tiles puzzle. Try to make an horizontal line of 10 blocks with no interruptions and it will disappear.

games.description: Enjoy this fun 3 card version of solitaire that adds bonus features and added challenge to the classic card game.

games.title: One More Sushi
games.description: Stack sushi and try to build the tallest sushi tower ever! Enjoy sweet graphics, 11 different sushi types and arcade mechanic that won't let you get bored!

games.title: Run Pig Run
games.description: Pig don't wants to be a sausage. Collect coins for play in casino where you can win bonuses for pig. In you'll see 7 unique power ups, beauty graphic and addictive gameplay. Please save the pig!!!

games.title: Black Jump
games.description: Escape the planet at war! Sprint through the derelict landscape, finish the enemies, avoid the deadly traps and collect the coins in this dynamic jump n run game.

games.title: 2048 Threes
games.description:
Welcome to the most successful game of the year - 2048 is the internet sensation! The 19 year old Gabriele Cirulli developed the game on just one weekend to find out if he can program a game from scratch. Since this moment the game has taken the internet by storm.
Playing 2048 is easy: Swipe to move all tiles from one side to another. If two tiles with the same value touch, they merge into one and add up their figures. The object of the game is to create a tile with a value of at least 2048. And if you finally manage to do so, you can try to push the limits and beat the best of the best players.

games.title: Brazil Cup 2014
games.description:
Grab the ball, put your jersey on and strap your shin guards - it is time to go out on the field an play football! Enjoy the world cup in this free online video game! If you think you know everything about football games, Brazilcup 2014 will be a pleasant surprise for you. Brazilcup 2014 is all about clever shots, avoiding obstacles  and using the environment to your advantage! In the end it's not important how you score, as long as you manage to fire the ball into the net.
Now choose your favorite team, practice unbelievable trick shots and finally take the cup with you in this great trick football game!

games.title: Ninjakira
games.description: It's a casual action beat em up game. Try to make as much combo as possible and survive hordes of ninja that blocking your way. Beat all of the missions and be the best Ninja in the Universe!

games.title: Candy Land
games.description: The friendly blue and red jellies need your help! Evil forces have blocked the way to their delicious lemonade and they are about to dry out! Save those by removing and replacing the yellow transparent blocks, moving bridges, pushing buttons and solving mind-bending levels of increasing difficulty that’ll keep you busy for hours in this challenging puzzle game. Candy Land is a wildly addictive puzzle game which once you’ve tried, you’ll be hooked! Try to solve over 28 different levels to save all friendly blue and red jellies. Don’t miss out - click to play now!

games.title: Spikes Ahead
games.description: Play against the clock by eliminating the blocks before they reach the spikey ceiling. Match 2 blocks to remove them, and match 6 or more to get a bonus bomb!

games.description: Switch, match items and do combos to achieve the objectives, play through the more than 25 highly interactive, bonus filled levels of this awesome looking match-3 puzzle game.

games.title: GTC Heat City
games.description: You run across the city in a car chase with the police officers. Collect repair items from the street to fix your damaged car but avoid other cars and roadblocks at all cost or the police wil get you!

games.title: Rebel Thumb
games.description: In this fast paced jump ’n’ run game a thumb decides to run off on it's own after being punished night after night on a joysticks and gamepads. Avoid obstacles and escape as long as you can in this fun game!

games.title: Sweet Garden
games.description: Try to create a chain reaction that pops all of the flowers But be careful, as you only have a few clicks available to clear the level, so dont waste any.

games.title: Flappy Bird Multiplayer
games.description: Fun, frustrating, addictive - this is Flappy Birds. While the developer took his masterpiece down from the app stores you can still enjoy it as a free online game. Fly and compete with other people from your area in this fun Flappy Bird mod! Carefully avoid the pipes and get further than anyone else, while you see the other players fail.

games.title: Words with Owl
games.description: Complete the words with the letters given below, make sure they are in the right order. Also try to make as much points as possible before time runs out so you can unlock more levels!

games.title: Candy Rain
games.description:
Candy Rain is back with 27 classic and 13 brand new levels! You have to match at least three candy's of the same type to make them disappear. Don’t rush your moves and always keep an eye on your score as in other match3 HTML5 games the turn limit is challenging and sometimes you need to plan a few moves ahead. To get a better score you should try to trigger combos and use as few moves as possible to accomplish the level goal. Unused moves will be turned into mighty boosters that shower you in bonus points after reaching the level goal. 
Play Candy Rain now for free and enjoy the sweets without having to think about the calories!

games.title: Furry Monster
games.description: Pop the furry monsters and trigger tremendous chain reactions, try to pop as many as you can in each level as you advance.

games.title: Twins Family
games.description: The twins in this fascinating puzzle game share a very special connection. If you bring them together they fusion together all the twins in the family to make them happy. Also grab the stars to get additional points!

games.title: Jelly Picnic
games.description:
Jelly Picnic is one of those games where you think you'll just play one quick round and then you don't stop playing for hours. Like the other Match-3 games, you have to make groups of three out of the jellies which then dissolve, making room for new pieces. If you're lucky, the new pieces match the existing ones, setting off a chain reaction and suddenly racking up your points.
If you combine more than three jellies of the same colour, they leave behind a bonus block that makes a whole row or colour vanish in seconds. And the clock that loads extra time onto the timer ticking away on every level is just as useful. Don't let the timer run out! Or back you go to level one – where you'll get caught over and over again trying again just one more, seriously just one more time this time...

games.title: Spiny Tom
games.description: Help Tom the hedgehog to get to the safety of his home! Memorize the way to Tom's home and while on the move grab as many apples as possible.

games.title: Jelly Monster

games.description: Beware, the zombie apocalypse did finally come. Fortunately you know how to avoid ever-hungry creatures - "Zombies can't jump". Prepare, grab your weapons and fight off the zombie invasion in this great and challenging tower defense game!
